our experimental setting, we use 1024 hidden units for MLPs, 1024 LSTM units and 512 latents. Our model is trained using learning rate of 0.001 and minibatches of size 32 and we set  =  = 1. A fully factorized multivariate Gaussian distribution is used as the output distribution. The final lower bound estimation on TIMIT can be found in Table 1.

